Chess piece artwork — Cburnett set
===================================

The inline SVG piece glyphs vendored in `src/pieces.rs` are derived from the
chess piece set created by Colin M. L. Burnett ("Cburnett") and published on
Wikimedia Commons (the `Chess_xxt45.svg` files, e.g. `Chess_klt45.svg`):

    https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:SVG_chess_pieces

The originals are multi-licensed; this crate uses them under the BSD license
below, as offered by the author on Wikimedia Commons.

Attribution: Colin M. L. Burnett.


